summary: Selene, portrayed by British actress Kate Beckinsale, is a fictional character and the main protagonist of the Underworld film series. More specifically, she serves as the central character in the films Underworld (2003), Underworld: Evolution (2006), Underworld: Awakening (2012), and Underworld: Blood Wars (2016).
